body.description: Let your baby make a splash with Huggies Little Swimmers swim diapers! Huggies Little Swimmers water diapers are made with unique materials that won't swell in water like regular baby diapers and deliver a comfortable fit, wet or dry. The Double Leak Guards of these disposable swim diapers fit snugly around your baby's legs to help contain messes and offer secure protection in the water. These Huggies diapers for swimming are designed to fit like swimwear and feature easy open, refastenable sides for an adjustable fit and quick diaper changes, whether you're at the pool or on the beach. The soft, stretchy waistband also makes these baby swim pants comfortable for your baby. These swimming diapers are also made with no harsh ingredients and are free of fragrances, lotions, elemental chlorine bleaching and natural rubber latex. Each pack features two Disney·Pixar Finding Nemo designs your child will love. Perfect for the pool, beach, splash park and more! Huggies Little Swimmers are available in sizes 3 Small (16-26 lbs), 4 Medium (24-34 lbs) and 5-6 Large (32+ lbs).

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These fit better when my child was closer to a size 6. They wear well under swim trunks and we have never had an accident in them while swimming. I love the tear feature because it is practically impossible to get them down when wet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My Big Girl loves them!!
reviews.reviewText: This review is going to be a little crazy. I have a giant schnauzer with a pee pee problem. She leaks in her sleep. So needless to say, she wears little swimmers and they work great. I put them on her hind legs like putting them on a baby and add a shoestring to cinch the side of diaper up over the top of her rump to keep them in place. They work great and hold a lot of moisture. Cheaper than buying doggie diapers. Thanks again Amazon!!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars LOVE huggies swimmers!
reviews.reviewText: I have tried sooo many different swim diapers and huggies take the lead by far! They fit my son the best, they absorb as much as they can, even if he goes #2 I barley know because of how well they lock it in, they are seriously so great!

reviews.reviewText: Fine for use under a bathing suit. Absorbent without expanding. Taped sides were a little tricky to unfurl and attach. Next time I might try the swim diapers that go on like pants and rip down the sides when it is time to come off.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Huggies are our favorite!
reviews.reviewText: Kid approved! We live on the lake & go to the beach often and my son loves his swim diapers.They're easy to slip on, the back is labeled (making it easy for the grandparents to know which way they go on too), and the sides pull apart when its time to remove them. These don't swell up huge like other brands we've tried. The hold in pee (and poo) great!These always make for a great time on the water, just wish they weren't so expensive.

I tried other disposable swim diapers but none have worked as good as these ones. They contain the "mess" and fit great. I also appreciate that they still have the velcro sides as well. I will be buying this brand from now on
